item.description: CPNG (Coupang, Inc.) Middle Coupang (NYSE:CPNG) may present a potential opportunity for investment, especially with the increase in its WOW membership and the overall impact of the COVID-19 pandemic on e-commerce. IQ (iQIYI, Inc.) Small iQIYI has significant growth potential due to its strong user base, diversified monetization model, and advanced technology, but it faces risks from competition, regulations, and cybersecurity threats.
